user
    - name, email, phone, password, addresses => [ ], age, image, status
    functions:
    --> password must stored in encrypted way
    --> mark logged in users
        - register
        - login
        - logout
        - profile
        - edit profile
        - deactivate 
        - activate

posts
    - content, file, type (image, video, txt),  user, comments => [{ user: , details: }], likes => [{ user }]
    functions:
        - add post => logged users only
        - show all posts
        - add comment
        - like or dislike post
